      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 604,
      "message": "Is there a special reason to return the entire collection? Consider moving the collection where it will be used. Because on the one hand, this class allows adding nodeTemplateId one-by-one to the internal set, but on the other hand it does nothing with the set (just returns it). You also expose the set to accidental modification by reference.",
